WEBVTT

00:00:02.780 --> 00:00:04.940
There's always the custom that when a person

00:00:09.940 --> 00:00:13.760
There was a person who used a wheelchair and

00:00:18.120 --> 00:00:21.320
When I die, I want them to put it inside the coffin.

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:30.466
And the family granted his wish. The day of the funeral

arrived, and the family buried him with his wheelchair.
00:00:31.420 --> 00:00:37.100
The second person was blind, and when he was about to die,

with all his family around his bed, he made his wish.
00:00:37.080 --> 00:00:40.420
I want that when I die, please, and the family granted it.

00:00:40.360 --> 00:00:46.326
When he died, at the funeral they buried the blind person

and placed his cane inside the coffin.
00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:53.700
And the third was an oral deaf person, and when he was about

to die with all his family he made his wish.
00:00:53.220 --> 00:00:55.600
I wish, and his family granted it.

00:00:55.520 --> 00:00:59.983
When they buried him, they put the cochlear implant and

the hearing aid inside the coffin.
00:01:01.340 --> 00:01:06.620
Then came a signing deaf person, and when he was about

to die, he made his wish, and they granted it.
00:01:06.720 --> 00:01:13.120
When the burial was held, they brought the live interpreter
